THE YIELD FROM THESE WELLS HAS BEEN GENERALLY FOUND TO BE IN THE RANGE OF 40 TO 60LPS. TERAI ZONE LIES BETWEEN BHABAR IN THE NORTH AND CENTRAL GANGA PLAIN IN THE SOUTH.
